Additionally, the paper's use of analytical hierarchy and decision problems suggests that it may also belong to the Discrete Mathematics (cs.DM) sub-category. The paper's focus on the cardinality of sets and its use of models of set theory suggests that it may also belong to the Computational Complexity (cs.CC) or Programming Languages (cs.PL) sub-categories.
